name: INVINCIBLE UNDER THE SUN[天下無双]
description: It is said the warrior's is the twofold Way of pen and sword, and he should have a taste for both Ways. Even if a man has no natural ability he can be a warrior by sticking assiduously to both divisions of the Way. Generally speaking, the Way of the warrior is resolute acceptance of death. - Miyamoto Musashi, Book of Five Rings
